---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Consulting"
  description="Consulting on AI literacy, Human-AI Interaction and psychologically informed AI adoption."
>
  <section class="page-shell">
    <header class="page-header">
      <div>
        <p class="eyebrow">Consulting</p>
        <h1>AI adoption needs psychological clarity.</h1>
      </div>
      <p>
        Prompted Psyche helps teams understand how AI changes trust, decision-making,
        communication and work practices.
      </p>
    </header>

    <div class="two-column">
      <div class="prose">
        <p>
          Consulting work is designed for organizations that want more than tooling advice.
          The focus is on human behavior around AI: how people overtrust systems, avoid
          them, negotiate responsibility, reshape communication and build new habits.
        </p>
        <p>
          Useful engagements can include expert briefings, AI literacy programs, research
          synthesis, interaction reviews, adoption risk mapping and advisory work for
          product or policy teams.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <div class="panel">
          <h3>Topics</h3>
          <ul class="plain-list">
            <li>AI literacy beyond prompt engineering</li>
            <li>Trust, reliance and automation bias</li>
            <li>Human-AI Interaction in workflows</li>
            <li>Communication norms around AI use</li>
            <li>Cyberpsychology-informed product thinking</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="panel">
          <h3>Best fit</h3>
          <p>
            Leadership teams, educators, product teams and organizations developing
            internal AI practices.
          </p>
          <div class="section-actions">
            <a class="button" href="/contact/">Start a conversation</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
